data.description: Listed below appraised value. Introducing a historic gem nestled in the heart of serene countryside living. This 3 bedroom, 1 bath home boasts timeless Southern charm and is situated on 25 wonderful acres (4 parcels being sold together), making it perfect for those seeking a tranquil escape or a unique development opportunity. The home features newer carpet and tile (2021), newer kitchen appliances (2021), and newer master bathroom (2020). The property has two wells (the back well is new), a new water softener, electricity, 2 small ponds, and a new 14-ton grain silo, catering to agricultural endeavors such as raising cattle. Creating smaller lots for development would be an easy task as well. An internet tower with fiber optics ensures connectivity for both the home and the separate 16X24 air-conditioned office that could be a guest room (recently remodeled), providing an ideal setting for remote work or a private retreat. Revel in the Florida lifestyle with a picturesque setting. There’s a 40’ x 80’ pole barn (recently installed) that could easily be converted to 12 stalls and a carport that is being used as a screened recreational room (24’ x 24’) for entertaining. Owners spent thousands of dollars on clearing and seeding a large chunk of the property (cleared 10 acres and grassed 2.5 acres). They also fenced 10 acres of the property. There used to be an arena on the property. The clay from the arena remains on the property. The property offers equestrian possibilities, allowing you to ride horses or ATVs across the expansive grounds. The absence of an HOA provides the freedom to shape the property to your dreams and desires. The property features public water nearby, making it feasible for development. With easy access to I-4, it’s just minutes away from the attractions, shopping, and restaurants, blending the allure of country life with modern conveniences. This unique estate presents an amazing opportunity to experience farm life, embrace the beauty of nature, and create your own paradise in the heart of Florida. Don’t miss the chance to own this one-of-a-kind property that seamlessly blends history, functionality, and the allure of the countryside.
